Haɗuwa mai yawa na cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya, 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020
Cigaban kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da United Kingdom ya tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa yana da matakai daban-daban dangane da ƙasa, cutar ta COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin dukkan ƙasashe.
Dangane da kwarewar da aka samu daga Italiya, jihohi, asibitoci da rukunin kula da gaggawa ya kamata su inganta shirye-shiryen su don karuwar adadin marasa lafiya da ke dauke da COVID-19 waɗanda za su buƙaci kulawar lafiya, musamman kulawar gaggawa.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu rahoton wani gungu na cutar huhu da ba a san asalinsa ba a Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa, kwayar cutar coronavirus ce wacce yanzu ake kira da coronavirus acute respiratory syndrome 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 an sanya mata sunan cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ya zuwa yanzu an tabbatar da cewa kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da rashin lafiya, watau kamuwa da numfashi tare da ko ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan marasa lafiya sun warke.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin dari na cutar, COVID-19 ta zama mafi muni da ke buƙatar kulawar asibiti yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin dari na cutar ta zama mai tsanani da ke buƙatar kulawa ta gaggawa.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4 cikin dari.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun tantance yanayin hawan COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai/Ƙasar Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da kuma United Kingdom (UK) kuma mun kwatanta su da lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya da na Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Al'ummar EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun kamu da cutar COVID-19
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya sami ƙarin yaduwar ƙasa da kuma yanayin cutar COVID-19 a duk duniya a halin yanzu bisa ga yanayin ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga bayanin WHO.
A EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton farkon mutane uku da suka kamu da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin waɗanda suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Ya zuwa ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da United Kingdom (UK), wanda tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da kuma wannan kwanan wata, an sami shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 da aka ruwaito, tare da 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kadai.
Samun adadin adadin mutane da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga tushe na hukuma kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta ƙasar, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, ana sabunta su kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a EU/EEA da Burtaniya, da kuma kwatanta shi da Italiya.
A matsayin wakili na yaduwar cutar COVID-19 mai aiki, mun ƙididdige adadin adadin adadin kwanaki 14 na COVID-19, saboda haka muna la'akari da hanyar COVID-19, a kowace EU/EEA da UK, a lokacin Janairu 1 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da aka ruwaito a kowace kasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a EU/EEA da UK
Yanayin a cikin kwanaki 14 na ƙididdigar adadin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK ya bi yanayin a Hubei Province (China) (Hoto 1).
Ga EU/EEA da Burtaniya gabaɗaya, adadin COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ya ƙaru sosai a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Abubuwan da aka ƙara).
Wannan ya samo asali ne daga karuwar yawan wadanda suka kamu da cutar daga Italiya, amma duk sauran kasashen EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan karuwar a kan adadin cutar COVID-19 (Additional Material).
Shafi na 2 ya nuna adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, a cikin EU/EEA da UK da kuma Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya jaddada cewa, har zuwa 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, sauran ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar kamar yadda Italiya ta yi makonni 3 ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin rahoton COVID-19 yana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya.
Yanayin yanayin COVID-19 da aka lura da shi yana nuna cewa cutar tana yaduwa a cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Duk da cewa ƙasashe suna kan matakai daban-daban, bambancin da ke cikin martani na lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa da ma'anar yiwuwar shari'ar na iya bambanta a cikin ƙasashe da kuma ka'idoji daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda dole ne a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin biye.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke dauke da cutar COVID-19 ke bukatar kulawa ta gaggawa kuma majiyoyin kafofin watsa labarai sun ruwaito cewa asibitoci da na'urorin kulawa ta gaggawa a yankin sun kai iyakar karfin su.
Bayanai kan shigar da COVID-19 a asibitoci da/ko na'urorin kulawa na gaggawa a halin yanzu suna nan a matakin EU/EEA don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'i, bi da bi (bayanai ba a nuna su ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a tattara bayanan a cikin tsari don tallafawa bayanan sa ido na yau da kullun da ke mai da hankali kan adadin waɗanda aka ba da rahoton da kuma adadin mutuwar.
Binciken da aka gudanar a 2010-11 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin wadatar gadajen kulawa da kulawa a Turai, tsakanin 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 gadaje ga kowane mazauna 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasar tana da fiye da ƙasa da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12.5 asibiti na asibiti da na kulawa na tsakiya don kowane mazauna 100,000 a 2010).
An samar da yanayin samfurin da ya danganci rashin wadatar kulawar lafiya, tare da kimantawa ga kowace EU/EEA da UK na yaduwar COVID-19 da aka kwantar a asibiti wanda ke da alaƙa da haɗarin > 90% fiye da ƙarfin gadajen kulawa, a cikin sabuntawa na shida na saurin kimanta haɗarin COVID-19 ta ECDC.
Tun da a yanzu haka an samu clusters a wasu yankuna a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya, kuma asibitoci da na'urorin kula da gaggawa suna kula da yawan mutanen da ke cikin yankin, ya kamata a samar da bayanai game da masu kamuwa da cutar da kuma gadajen kula da gaggawa a Tatanama don na'urorin kula da gaggawa na matakin 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewa daga Italiya da kuma yanayin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe ya nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, dole ne ƙasashe, asibitoci da rukunin kulawa ta gaggawa su shirya don yanayin watsawa na SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma karuwar adadin marasa lafiya da ke kamuwa da COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta kiwon lafiya, musamman kulawa ta gaggawa, kamar yadda ke faruwa a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka jaddada a cikin sabon ƙimar haɗarin ECDC, hanzari, mai himma da cikakkiyar hanya tana da mahimmanci don rage saurin watsa SARS-CoV-2, tare da motsawa daga hanyar hanawa zuwa ragewa, saboda tsammanin saurin ƙaruwa a cikin adadin shari'o'in na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, karɓa da daidaita martani yadda ya kamata idan ba a aiwatar da su ba da wuri.
Binciken hadarin da aka yi cikin gaggawa ya kuma lissafa matakan kiwon lafiya na jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokacin da ƙasashe ke da damar ci gaba da haɓaka ƙoƙarin sarrafa su don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan wannan ya gaza, yana yiwuwa tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA zai fuskanci karuwar marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai mahimmanci a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Barkewar cutar Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), wanda cutar SARS ta haifar, ya kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ya cutar da mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran sassan duniya, wanda hakan ya haifar da bala'i ga bil'adama.
Kamar yadda kwayar cutar ta SARS-CoV, wacce ta haifar da SARS a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya yaduwa daga batutuwan kuma yana haifar da alamun bayyanar ta hanyar irin wannan hanyar.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙarancin tsananin cutar da ƙarancin mutuwar SARS amma yana da saurin yaduwa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata.
Domin a san cewa ana yawan wallafa wannan sabon ciwo, an yi ƙoƙari a ba da cikakken bayani game da wannan ciwo da ake ci gaba da bincike a kai.
Za mu tattauna muhimman abubuwa game da cutar, da yadda ake kamuwa da ita, da yadda ake kamuwa da ita, da yadda ake gane ta, da yadda ake kula da ita, da yadda ake gane ta, da kuma yadda za a hana ta.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da za a amsa, muna fatan cewa wannan bita zai taimaka wajen fahimtar da kuma kawar da wannan cuta mai barazana.
Bikin bazara a ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa da ba a zata ba ga mutanen China da aka bukaci su zauna a gida a lokacin hutun da makonni bayan haka saboda barkewar cutar kwayar cutar.
Kwayar cutar ta yi kama da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) da ta haifar da barkewar cutar ta saurin numfashi (SARS) a 2003; saboda haka, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanya mata suna SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu 2020 kuma ta sanya mata sunan cutar CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Wannan annobar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China kuma ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa duk kasar da kusan wasu kasashe 50 a duniya.
Ya zuwa ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, kwayar cutar ta haifar da sama da 80,000 na tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, tare da sama da marasa lafiya 40,000 da aka sallame su gida da kuma sama da marasa lafiya 3,000 da suka mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine "magabcin jama'a na 1" kuma yana da damar zama mai ƙarfi fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga takardu sama da 2000 game da COVID-19 gami da ilimin kwayar cuta, ilimin cututtuka, ilimin asali, ganewar asali da magani tun bayan rahoton farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 wanda ya ƙayyade kwayar cutar da aka ware daga wasu marasa lafiya.
Wannan bita ya yi ƙoƙari ya taƙaita ci gaban bincike a cikin sabon yanki da kuma ci gaba da sauri.
A lokacin da ya dace, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wani cuta da ke haifar da CoV, ciwon numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, wanda ya ɓarke a shekara ta 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da aka sani game da rigakafin cutar da kuma yadda za a iya gane ta, da kuma wasu muhimman tambayoyi.
CoVs an saba ganin su a matsayin masu cutarwa marasa lahani ga mutane, yawanci su ne ke haifar da kusan kashi 15% na mura ta yau da kullun 4.
Duk da haka, a wannan ƙarni, mun gano kwayar cutar mutum mai saurin kamuwa da cuta sau biyu, wato SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da barkewar annobar da ta samo asali a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabiya a 2012, kuma nan da nan ta bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa tare da mummunan yanayin rashin lafiya da mutuwa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine annoba ta uku ta CoV a tarihin ɗan adam da aka rubuta.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin Hoto na 1,1, an fara bayar da rahoton tarin cutar huhu da ba a san asalinsa ba daga Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 ga Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta China.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an fitar da kwayar cutar.
A ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020 an samu rahoton mutuwar mutum na farko daga Wuhan.
A halin yanzu, annobar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa birane, larduna da ƙasashe makwabta.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an samu rahoton kamuwa da cuta a tsakanin ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya, wanda ke nuna cewa mutum-zuwa-mutum na iya faruwa.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an sanya dokar hana fita a birnin Wuhan, inda aka dakatar da dukkan ayyukan sufuri.
A ranar 24 ga Janairu binciken farko na asibiti kan cutar ya ruwaito cewa, daga cikin marasa lafiya 41 da aka tabbatar da su, 21 ne kawai suka yi hulɗa kai tsaye da kasuwar abincin teku ta Wuhan wanda ake ganin shine farkon fara kamuwa da cutar daga asalin dabbobi da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, WHO ta ayyana cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta duniya.
A lokacin wannan rahoton, cutar ta bazu ko'ina cikin kasar Sin da kuma kusan wasu kasashe 50 a duniya (Shirya (Shirya 2).2).
Saboda yadda lamarin ke ci gaba da bunkasa, ba a san ko cutar za ta kai ko za ta yi tsanani ba.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, nazarin cibiyoyi da yawa na marasa lafiya 8,866 ciki har da 4,021 waɗanda aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 sun ba da ƙarin bayani game da annobar kamar haka (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 na kamuwa da marasa lafiya a duk shekaru, amma mafi yawansu suna tsakanin shekaru 30-65.
Kusan rabin (47.7%) na waɗanda suka kamu da cutar sun haura shekaru 50, kaɗan ne ke ƙasa da shekaru 20 kuma mutane 14 ne kawai suka kamu da cutar da shekarunsu ba su kai 10 ba.
SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da maza da yawa (0.31/100,000) fiye da mata (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 na yaduwa a cikin gidajen abinci da ke da yawa a cikin da kewaye da Hubei.
COVID-19 yana ɗaukar matsakaicin kwanaki 5 (2-9) daga farkon zuwa ganewar asali.
Matsakaicin lokacin jinkiri shine kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
Matsakaicin lokaci daga farawa zuwa mutuwa shine 9.5 (4.8-13) kwanaki.
Lambar haihuwa (R0) na asali shine 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51-4.05), kuma daidaitaccen RO shine 2.23-4.82.
Adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ya karu sosai kafin 23 ga Janairu, 2020, daidai da lokacin manyan motsi kafin bikin bazara a China.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya tare da tabbatar da shari'ar shine 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%), kuma daidaitaccen mutuwar ga dukkan marasa lafiya shine 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Abubuwa uku na farko da ke haifar da COVID-19 su ne jinsi (maza), shekaru (≥60) da kuma ciwon huhu mai tsanani.
CoVs wani ƙaramin kwayar cuta ne mai girma da ke ɗauke da zaren RNA guda ɗaya.
Ana iya rarraba kwayar cutar zuwa nau'i huɗu, wato, alpha, beta, gamma, da delta, a tsakanin dukkan alpha- da beta-CoVs da aka sani da cutar ɗan adam.
Spike (S) glycoprotein surface yana ɗaure ga masu karɓar ƙwayar cuta na angiotensin-modifying enzyme 2 (ACE2) da dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) don SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, kuma daga baya membrane fusion yana faruwa.
