Wannan sakon ya sauƙaƙa damuwa a cikin jama'a, musamman a lokacin da duk ƙasar ke shirin bikin bazara, kuma ba za a iya karɓar shi ba don hana yaduwar cutar a Wuhan.
Hukumar kula da cututtuka a China na iya koyon darasi daga wannan kuma su inganta a nan gaba.
Misali, hukumomi masu dacewa (1) sun fi taka tsantsan wajen sanar da jama'a saboda kowane bayani da aka gabatar yana tasiri kan halayen jama'a da yanke shawara; (2) sun fi jin dadi da kuma amsawa ga bayanai na musamman da aka samu daga asibiti fiye da jiran rahoto na yau da kullun daga likitoci ko jami'ai; (3) sun fi tsauri wajen hana barkewar cutar fiye da kwantar da hankalin jama'a; da (4) gudanar da atisaye akai-akai don kara wayar da kan jama'a game da cutar ta annoba da kuma gwadawa da kuma inganta tsarin mayar da martani na jama'a akai-akai.
Cutar COVID-19 ta samo asali ne daga kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 da ta fara a ƙarshen Disamba 2019.
A cikin kasa da watanni biyu, ya yaɗu a duk ƙasar Sin da kuma kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya a lokacin da nake rubuta wannan.
Tun da yake kwayar cutar ta yi kama da SARS-CoV kuma alamun cutar sun yi kama da na SARS, yaduwar COVID-19 ta haifar da jin cewa annobar SARS ta sake faruwa.
Duk da haka, akwai bambance-bambance masu mahimmanci tsakanin COVID-19 da SARS, waɗanda ke da mahimmanci wajen hana annobar da kuma kula da marasa lafiya.
COVID-19 ya shafi tsofaffi fiye da matasa kuma ya fi rinjayar maza fiye da mata, kuma tsananin cutar da mutuwar mutane sun fi tsofaffi fiye da matasa.
SARS yana da yawan mutuwar da ya fi na COVID-19 (10.91% vs. 1.44%).
Marasa lafiya na COVID-19 na iya yada kwayar cutar ba tare da samun wata alama ba yayin da masu cutar SARS ke yada kwayar cutar a cikin yanayin rashin lafiya, wanda ke haifar da wahalar hana yaduwar COVID-19 fiye da SARS.
Wannan ya bayyana dalilin da yasa SARS-CoV-2 ke yaduwa cikin sauri da kuma yaduwa fiye da SARS-CoV.
Sakamakon gwajin RNA na SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama mara kyau ga marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
Duk da haka, waɗanda suka warke za su iya sake kamuwa da cutar.
Wannan binciken ya kara hadarin kamuwa da cutar kai tsaye.
Dangane da saurin ci gaba a cikin binciken COVID-19, wasu batutuwa masu mahimmanci har yanzu suna buƙatar a bincika, gami da:
Daga ina SARS-CoV-2 ya fito?
Ko da yake an gano kashi 96% na kwayoyin halittar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma CoVs biyu kamar SARS na bat, ba za mu iya kammala cewa SARS-CoV-2 ma daga bat ne ya fito ba.
Shin dabbobi ne suke watsa kwayar cutar daga gida, kamar su bat, zuwa ga mutane?
Idan ba mu san amsoshin tambayoyin farko da na biyu ba, ba za mu iya magance cutar ba, kuma za ta iya sake faruwa a kowane lokaci.
Ko da yake gwajin samfurin kwayoyin halitta da kuma nazarin kwayoyin sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da alaƙa da ACE2, ta yaya kwayar cutar za ta iya shiga cikin ƙwayoyin iska kuma ta haifar da canje-canje na pathology?
Shin kwayar cutar tana da alaƙa da ƙwayoyin bayyana ACE2 a wasu gabobin jiki?
Idan ba tare da amsar wannan tambayar ba, ba za mu iya samun ganewar asali da kuma ingantaccen magani ba.
Har yaushe za a ci gaba da wannan annoba?
Ta yaya wannan kwayar cutar ta samu ci gaba ta hanyar kwayar halitta a tsakanin mutane?
Shin za ta zama annoba ta duniya, ta ƙare kamar SARS ko kuma za ta sake faruwa a kai a kai kamar mura?
Wannan yana da muhimmanci amma zai ɗauki lokaci kafin a sami amsoshin waɗannan tambayoyin da kuma wasu da yawa.
Duk da haka, duk da irin tsadar da za a iya kashewa, ba mu da wani zaɓi sai dai mu dakatar da annobar da wuri-wuri kuma mu mayar da rayuwarmu ga al'ada.
Tushen kwayar cutar coronavirus na mutum
Juyin halitta da kuma daidaitawa sun haifar da juyin halitta tare da coronavirus (CoV) da kuma manyan rundunoninsa, ciki har da mutane, tsawon dubban shekaru.
Kafin 2003, an san cewa kwayar cutar mutum (HCoV) biyu tana haifar da cututtuka masu saurin kamuwa da cuta, kamar mura.
Annobar cutar sankara ta SARS da ta MERS ta sauya ra'ayi kuma ta nuna yadda cutar HCoVs take da hatsari da kuma barazana ga rai.
Bayyanar SARS-CoV-2 a China a ƙarshen 2019 ya jawo hankalin CoV kuma ya ba mu mamaki game da sauƙin kamuwa da cuta amma ba shi da cutarwa kamar SARS-CoV.
Cutar HCoVs zoonosis ce kuma fahimtar asalin kwayar cutar HCoVs na iya taimaka mana.
Yawancin kwayar cutar HCoVs sun fito ne daga barbashi wanda ba shi da cutar.
An kuma san wani mai watsa shiri na matsakaici na wasu HCoVs.
Gano kwayar dabbobi yana da tasiri kai tsaye kan rigakafin cutar ɗan adam.
Binciken game da hulɗar mai watsa CoV a cikin dabbobi ya ba da damar fahimtar mahimmancin cutar CoV a cikin ɗan adam.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun gabatar da cikakken bayani game da ilimin da ake da shi game da kwayar cutar HCoV guda bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su da asalin zoonotic da watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
Abin da ya fi muhimmanci shi ne, mun gwada kuma mun bambanta HCoVs daga mahangar juyin halitta na ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halitta.
An tattauna game da cutar COVID-19 a wannan mahallin.
Bugu da kari, an jaddada bukatar samun nasarar musayar masaukin baki da kuma tasirin juyin halittar kwayar cutar kan tsananin cutar.
Kwayar cuta ta coronavirus (CoV) tana cikin dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi rukuni guda na ƙwayoyin cuta masu amfani da RNA masu amfani da jini.
Wannan kwayar halitta tana da tsawon tsakanin kilobase 26 zuwa 32 kuma ita ce mafi girma a cikin kwayar cutar RNA kuma an sanya mata suna "CoV" saboda siffar da take da ita kamar kambi a karkashin na'urar duba siginar lantarki.
A tsarin, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halittar da ba su da sashi da suka yi kama da juna.
An kiyasta cewa kashi biyu bisa uku na wannan kwayoyin suna da manyan manyan tsarin karatu guda biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b) wadanda suka yi aiki tare, wanda daga baya aka fassara zuwa pp1a da pp1ab polyprotein replicase.
Bayan haka, ana sarrafa polyprotein don samar da 16 da ba a tsara su ba, wanda ake kira nsp1~16.
Sauran kwayoyin sun hada da ORFs don sunadaran da aka tsara, ciki har da gashi (S), sheqa (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
Wasu sunadarai na musamman na sunadarai sun hada da wasu sunadarai na musamman na CoV.
Dangane da bambancin jerin sunadarai, CoVs an rarraba su zuwa nau'ikan hudu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV da delta-CoV), inda beta-CoVs suka ƙunshi yawancin HCoVs kuma an raba su zuwa jerin hudu (A, B, C da D).
Shaidar phylogenetic ta nuna cewa bat da beraye suna aiki a matsayin tushen kwayoyin zuwa mafi yawan alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye su ne babban wurin ajiyar gamma-CoVs da delta-coVs.
A cikin dubban shekaru, CoVs sun sha kan nau'in rigakafi kuma wasu sun bayyana a matsayin muhimman cututtukan ɗan adam.
Ya zuwa yanzu, an gano kwayar cutar korona ta mutum guda bakwai.
Daga cikinsu akwai HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 wanda shine alpha-CoV.
Sauran beta-CoVs guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, cutar sankarar hankula (SARS-CoV), cutar sankarar hankula ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV) da kuma SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 yawanci suna haifar da alamun rashin lafiya, kamar sanyi da/ko diarrhea.
A gefe guda, sabon SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 sun kasance masu cutarwa sosai, suna haifar da kamuwa da cuta mai tsanani a cikin ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi a cikin marasa lafiya waɗanda ke da babban yiwuwar samun cututtukan cututtukan numfashi (ARDS) da kuma bayyanar extrapulmonary.
An ware kwayar HCoV-229E ta farko, B814, daga hanci na marasa lafiya da ke fama da mura a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sami ƙarin sani ta hanyar nazarin da aka yi game da HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, dukansu sun haifar da alamun rigakafin kai.
An yarda da ra'ayin cewa kamuwa da kwayar HCoV ba shi da haɗari har sai barkewar cutar SARS.
Yaduwar cutar SARS ta faru a 2003 kuma ta kasance daya daga cikin munanan lalacewar tarihi, ta cutar da mutane sama da 8,000 tare da yawan mutuwar mutane kusan 10%.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, annobar cutar MERS ta haifar da ci gaba da barkewar cutar a yankin Larabawa tare da yaduwar ta a wasu wurare a duniya.
Sabuwar kwayar cutar HCoV 2019 (2019-nCoV), daga baya aka sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2, ita ce ta haifar da annobar annobar cutar coronavirus ta 2010 (COVID-1), wacce ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 3,120 da kuma kamuwa da mutane 91,000 a ranar 3 ga Maris, 2020.
An yi gargadi kuma duniya ta shirya don fuskantar cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Dukkanin kwayar cutar HCoVs bakwai suna da asalin zoonotic daga bat, mice da dabbobi.
Akwai tabbaci mai yawa da ke nuna cewa HCoVs sun samo asali ne daga namomin kaza, inda kwayar cutar take da sauƙin daidaitawa kuma ba ta haifar da cuta ba amma tana nuna bambancin kwayoyin halitta.
Cutar COVID-2019 ta kawo babbar kalubale ta likita, kimiyya, zamantakewa da ɗabi'a ga China da sauran duniya.
Binciken asalin kwayar cutar HCoV ya ba da tsari don fahimtar tarihin halitta, motsawa da abubuwan da ke hana tsalle-tsalle na nau'in.
Hakanan yana iya jagorantar da sauƙaƙe binciken mai watsa labaran dabbobi, masu matsakaici da masu ɗaukar hoto don SARS-CoV-2, tare da mahimman abubuwan da ke tattare da hana yaduwar a nan gaba.
A cikin wannan bita mun gabatar da cikakken bayani game da asalin zoonotic, watsawa tsakanin jinsuna da kuma cutar HCoV.
Musamman, mun tsara kuma mun tattauna batun da aka saba da shi inda kwayar cutar HCoV ba ta da cutar a cikin ɗakunan ajiyar halitta amma ta zama mai cutar bayan kamuwa da nau'in zuwa sabon mai watsa shiri.
Mun kuma sake nazarin yanayin juyin HCoVs inda yawanci ana samun karuwar yaduwar cuta tare da raguwar cutar.
Sakamakon barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2 da ke gudana an kuma tattauna shi a cikin wannan mahallin.
An san kwayar cutar dabbobi tun daga ƙarshen 1930s.
Kafin warewar farko na kwayar HCoV-229E B814 daga hancin masu fama da cutar sanyi, an ware CoVs daban-daban a cikin dabbobi da dama da suka kamu da cutar, ciki har da kaza, beraye, shanu, aladu, kuliyoyi da karnuka.
A cikin shekarun da suka gabata, an gano kwayar cutar HCoV guda bakwai.
Takaitaccen tarihin gano HCoV a cikin tsarin lokaci (Table 1) na iya ba da bayani da koyarwa.
An fara ware kwayar HCoV-229E daga cikin numfashi na marasa lafiya da ke fama da kamuwa da cuta a cikin numfashi na sama a 1966, kuma an sake tsara ta don girma a cikin layin kwayar cutar huhu WI-38.
Marasa lafiya da ke kamuwa da HCoV-229E suna nuna alamun cutar, ciki har da ciwon kai, tari, laushi da ciwon makogwaro, tare da zazzabi da tari da aka gani a cikin 10~20% na lokuta.
Daga baya a 1967, an ware HCoV-OC43 daga al'adun gabobin jiki sannan kuma an yi jerin abubuwan da ke cikin kwakwalwar linzamin kwamfuta.
Bayanan asibiti na kamuwa da HCoV-OC43 sun yi kama da kamuwa da HCoV-229E, wanda ba shi da bambanci daga kamuwa da wasu cututtukan cututtukan numfashi kamar su kwayar cutar mura A da rhinovirus.
Dukansu HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 suna yaduwa a duniya kuma suna da saurin yaduwa a lokacin hunturu a yankunan da ke da yanayin zafi.
Yawancin lokaci, tsawon lokacin da ake hana cutar da kuma cutar da ita ba su kai mako guda ba, sai kuma a yi rashin lafiya na tsawon makonni biyu.
Bisa ga binciken da aka yi kan masu sa kai na ɗan adam, mutane masu lafiya da suka kamu da HCoV-229E sun sami saurin kamuwa da cutar.
Wasu marasa lafiya da suka kamu da cutar sun nuna cewa suna da ciwon numfashi mai tsanani.
SARS, wanda kuma aka sani da atypical pneumonia, shi ne annoba ta farko da HCoV ya haifar da shi wanda aka rubuta shi a tarihin ɗan adam kuma mai maganin cutar shine SARS-CoV, HCoV na uku da aka gano.
An gano farkon cutar SARS a ƙarshen 2002 a lardin Guangdong na kasar Sin.
Cutar SARS ta haifar da kamuwa da cutar 8,096 da kuma mutuwar mutane 774, a kasashe da nahiyoyi da dama.
Baya ga super-spreader, an kiyasta cewa kowane yanayi na iya haifar da kusan yanayi biyu na biyu, tare da lokacin jinkiri tsakanin kwanaki 4 zuwa 7 kuma yanayin da ba shi da kwayar cutar ya bayyana a ranar 10 na cutar.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da SARS-CoV da farko suna nuna rashin tausayi, ciwon kai, zazzabi, zazzabi da sanyi, sannan kuma dyspnea, tari da kuma damuwa na numfashi a matsayin alamun bayyanar.
Lymphophenia, gwajin aikin hanta da ya ɓace da kuma ƙaruwa a cikin sinadarin creatine kinase, su ne abubuwan da ba su dace ba a cikin gwajin SARS.
An kuma lura da lalacewar alveolar difus, haɓakar ƙwayoyin epithelium da haɓaka macrophage a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS.
Kusan kashi 20-30% na marasa lafiya suna bukatar kulawa mai kyau da kuma na'ura mai aiki da iska.
Baya ga kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar numfashi, wasu gabobin jiki da suka hada da gastrointestinal tract, hanta da koda na iya kamuwa da cutar a cikin wannan mawuyacin hali, wanda yawanci yakan zo tare da tashin cytokine, wanda zai iya haifar da mutuwa musamman a cikin marasa lafiya masu rauni.
An fara ware kwayar cutar ne daga kwayar cutar huhu ta budewa da aka yi wa wani dan uwan wani mai cutar da ke tafiya zuwa Hong Kong daga Guangzhou.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an yi ƙoƙari sosai don binciken HCoV.
An ware HCoV-NL63 daga wani yaro mai wata 7 daga Netherlands a ƙarshen 2004.
Da farko an gano cewa cutar ta yadu a cikin yara, tsofaffi da kuma marasa lafiya masu rauni na numfashi.
Kasancewar tari, conjunctivitis, zazzabi da bronchiolitis na yau da kullun ne a cikin cututtukan da HCoV-NL63 ke haifarwa.
Wani bincike na 'yanci ya bayyana cewa an cire irin wannan kwayar cutar daga hanci na wani yaro mai wata takwas da ke fama da ciwon huhu a Netherlands.
Ko da yake an gano shi a Netherlands, amma a zahiri ya yadu a duk duniya.
An kiyasta cewa HCoV-NL63 shine ke haifar da kimanin kashi 4.7% na cututtukan numfashi na yau da kullun kuma lokacin mafi girma na cutar shine farkon bazara, bazara da hunturu.
HCoV-NL63 yana da alaƙa da cutar laringitis na hanawa, wanda kuma ake kira croup.
A wannan shekarar, an ware HCoV-HKU1 daga wani mutum mai shekaru 71 da aka kwantar da shi a asibiti da ciwon huhu da kuma cutar sankarar bargo a Hong Kong.
Baya ga cutar huhu da kuma cutar sankarar bargo da ke kamuwa da ita a cikin al'umma, an kuma bayar da rahoton cewa HCoV-HKU1 yana da alaƙa da matsanancin tashin hankali na asma.
Kamar yadda HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 ana samun su a duk duniya, suna haifar da rashin lafiya na numfashi.
Dukkanin HCoVs huɗu da aka kamu da su a cikin al'ummar sun daidaita da mutane kuma ba su da wataƙila ta hanyar canzawa zuwa cutar da ke haifar da cututtuka, kodayake haɗarin ya faru ne saboda ba a san dalilin ba saboda akwai ƙananan lokuta na cutar HCoV-NL63, wanda kwanan nan aka ba da rahoton cewa ya haifar da mummunan kamuwa da cutar numfashi a cikin China.
Gabaɗaya, lokacin da wannan HCoV ya sami damar yaduwa cikin inganci kuma ya kasance cikin jikin mutum, wannan kwayar cutar ma ta zama mai cutarwa ko rashin cutarwa.
An fara ware kwayar cutar MERS-CoV a shekarar 2012 daga huhu na wani mutum mai shekaru 60 da ke fama da ciwon huhu da kuma rashin aikin koda a Saudi Arabia.
Duk da cewa yawancin lab-tabbatattun shari'o'in sun fito ne daga Gabas ta Tsakiya, an samu rahoton shigo da shari'o'in tare da wasu lokuta na watsawa ta hanyar kusanci a kasashen Turai da Tunisia.
Wani kuma barkewar cutar ta biyu ya faru ne a Koriya ta Kudu a shekarar 2015 inda aka tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar mutum 186.
Bayyanar asibiti ga MERS tana kama da SARS, wanda ke nuna ci gaba da ciwon huhu mai tsanani.
Ba kamar SARS ba, yawancin marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar MERS suna fama da rashin aikin koda, wanda har yanzu ya zama na musamman ga MERS a cikin cututtukan da HCoVs ke haifarwa.
Fiye da kashi 30 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya suna nuna alamun ciwon ciki, kamar su diarrhea da kuma amai.
Ya zuwa 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, sama da lambobi 2500 da aka tabbatar da su an bayar da rahoton su tare da mutuwar mutum 34.4%, wanda ya sanya MERS-CoV daya daga cikin cututtukan da suka fi addabar mutane.
A tsakiyar zuwa ƙarshen Disamba 2019, an gano wani gungu na masu fama da cutar huhu da aka sani a baya dangane da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana annobar cutar numfashi ta SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin Matsalar Lafiya ta Duniya kuma ta sanya sunan cutar COVID-19.
Ya zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020, an sami rahotanni 90,053 a duniya, tare da mutuwar mummunan yanayin kashi 3.4%.
Abin lura, mutuwar cutar a Hubei, China ya kai kashi 4.2%, yayin da mutuwar cutar a waje da yankin ya kai kashi 1.2%.
SARS-CoV-2 na haifar da cututtukan numfashi masu tsanani kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, suna bayyana a matsayin zazzabi, tari da kuma dyspnea.
Wasu marasa lafiya ma suna da ciwon hauka.
Ciwon huhu yana cikin munanan alamu kuma yana iya ƙaruwa da sauri zuwa ciwon numfashi mai tsanani.
Kodayake SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 suna da kamanceceniya sosai saboda babban daidaiton nucleotide na 82%, kwayar cutar ta rarrabu zuwa rassa daban-daban a kan bishiyar phylogenetic.
SARS-CoV-2 ya bayyana ba shi da cutar amma yana da saurin yaduwa fiye da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
An samu rahotanni na mutane da ke dauke da cutar SARS-CoV-2 kuma hakan na iya haifar da saurin yaduwar cutar a duniya.
Kwatanta SARS-CoV-2 da sauran HCoVs shida ya nuna kamance da bambance-bambance masu ban sha'awa.
Na farko, lokacin ragewa da tsawon lokacin cutar HCoV suna da kama sosai.
A wannan yanayin, SARS-CoV-2 ya bi halin da sauran HCoVs shida suka kasance.
Na biyu, cutar COVID-19 tana da alamun cutar tsakanin SARS-CoV da kuma HCoVs guda huɗu da aka samo daga al'umma (cf. HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63).
A gefe guda, kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 yana nuna halaye da aka fi gani yayin kamuwa da HCoVs da aka samo daga al'umma, gami da kasancewar rashin takamaiman, rashin ƙarfi ko rashin alamun bayyanar cututtuka.
A wani bangare kuma, ana iya ganin karamin rukunin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 kamar yadda ake ganin SARS-CoV, kodayake a ɗan ƙarami.
Na uku, yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 ta kuma nuna halaye masu ban sha'awa ga duka HCoVs da aka samo daga al'umma da SARS-CoV.
A wani bangare, cutar SARS-CoV-2 tana da cutarwa aƙalla kamar yadda HCoVs suke da su daga al'umma.
A gefe guda, yana da wuya a tabbatar ko cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta ragu bayan ta wuce ta hanyar mutane kamar yadda ya faru a cikin SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
A ƙarshe, kamar sauran HCoVs, ana iya gano SARS-CoV-2 a cikin samfurin fitsari.
Ko watsawa ta hanyar hanci zuwa baki don SARS-CoV-2 yana taka muhimmiyar rawa kamar yadda yake a cikin yanayin SARS-CoV aƙalla a ƙarƙashin wasu yanayi yana jiran bayani ta hanyar nazarin gaba.
Yana da ban sha'awa kuma a ga ko SARS-CoV-2 na iya yaduwa ta yanayi kamar yadda yake a cikin yanayin HCoVs da ke kamuwa da cutar a cikin al'umma.
Duk da haka, halayen SARS-CoV-2 ciki har da kamuwa da cuta, cutar da ke haifar da cutar da kuma ci gaba da yaduwa bayan ta hanyar mutane zai shafi ƙarshen annobar COVID-19 da ke gudana.
Dukkanin HCoVs huɗu da suka kamu da cutar a cikin al'umma sun haifar da rashin alamun cutar kuma sun dace da mutane.
A wani bangare kuma, yana iya zama gaskiya cewa mutane sun daidaita da kyau ga waɗannan HCoVs huɗu.
A wasu kalmomi, dukansu sun tsira daga annobar HCoV na baya.
An kawar da kwayar cutar HCoV mai saurin kamuwa da cuta a cikin mutane da kuma mutane masu kamuwa da cutar HCoV mai tsanani.
Don a yi hakan, HCoVs dole ne su ninka a cikin mutane har zuwa isasshen matakin da zai ba da damar tattara canjin da ke adawa da abubuwan da ke hana mai masaukin baki.
