Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana annobar COVID-19 mai gudana  cutar da ke haifar da kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2  a matsayin annoba.
Ko da yake kalmar "annoba" tana nufin yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda cutar take da hatsari ba, WHO ta fahimci bukatar karfafawa gwamnatoci gwiwa su dauki mataki:
Dukkanin kasashe na iya sauya yanayin annobar.
Idan kasashen suka gano, gwada, kula, ware, bi da kuma motsa mutanensu su dauki mataki, in ji Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Darakta Janar na WHO.
Muna matukar damuwa game da matakin yaduwar cutar da kuma tsananin rashin aiki.
Wani tsohon darektan Hukumar Kula da Cututtuka a Amirka, Dr. Tom Frieden ya ce, annobar "ba ta taɓa faruwa ba".
Ya ce, a cikin wani labarin da CNN ta wallafa a watan Fabrairu, "ban da mura, babu wata kwayar cutar numfashi da aka gano daga fitowar zuwa yaduwar yaduwar duniya".
Ghebreyesus ya bayyana irin wannan ra'ayi, yana cewa "ba mu taɓa ganin annobar da coronavirus ta haifar ba".
Ya ci gaba, "kuma ba mu taɓa ganin wata annoba da za a iya sarrafawa a lokaci ɗaya ba".
Sabon matsayin da aka ba da cutar ya biyo bayan shawarar da WHO ta yanke a watan Janairu na ayyana annobar a matsayin gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a a duniya.
Daraktan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Ciwo na Ƙasa ta Amirka, Dokta Anthony Fauci, ya ce game da annobar, "a taƙaice, za ta ƙara muni".
Kamar yadda na jiya Alhamis, Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya ruwaito akwai aƙalla mutane 126,000 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a duniya, inda suka yi mutuwar mutane fiye da 4,600.
Cutar cutar coronavirus ta 201920 ita ce cutar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda ke gudana, wadda ta haifar da cutar coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
An gano annobar a Wuhan, China, a watan Disamba na 2019, an ayyana ta a matsayin Matsalar Lafiya ta Duniya a ranar 30 ga Janairu, 2020, kuma an ayyana ta a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya zuwa 10 ga Afrilu 2020, an samu rahoton kimanin mutane miliyan 1.61 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kasashe 210 da yankuna, wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 97,000.
