An sanar da shirin rage zirga-zirgar tsakanin biranen a watan Maris, duk da cewa cunkoson zirga-zirgar tsakanin biranen kafin bikin Sabuwar Shekarar Farisa ya ci gaba.
Cin abinci na Shi'a a Qom ya kasance a bude ga masu ziyara har zuwa 16 ga Maris, 2020. Iran ta zama cibiyar yaduwar cutar bayan China a watan Fabrairu.
Duk da zargin cewa cutar ta yadu a Iran, sama da kasashe goma sun gano ko sun dawo da cutar zuwa Iran a ranar 28 ga watan Fabrairu, wanda ke nuna cewa cutar ta fi ta 388 da gwamnatin Iran ta ruwaito a ranar.
An rufe majalisar dokokin Iran, inda aka ce 23 daga cikin mambobinta 290 sun kamu da cutar a ranar 3 ga watan Maris.
A ranar 12 ga watan Maris, Human Rights Watch ta bukaci hukumomin gidan yarin Iran da su saki 'yan gwagwarmayar kare hakkin dan adam da aka tsare saboda zanga-zangar lumana ba tare da wani sharadi ba, da kuma sakin dukkan fursunonin da suka cancanci su zauna na dan lokaci.
Ya ce akwai babban hadarin kamuwa da kwayar cutar a cikin gidajen da aka rufe kamar cibiyoyin tsare mutane, wanda kuma ke da karancin kulawar lafiya.
A ranar 15 ga watan Maris, gwamnatin Iran ta bayar da rahoton mutuwar mutane 100 a rana, wanda shi ne mafi yawan wadanda suka mutu a kasar tun bayan barkewar cutar.
Akalla 'yan siyasa 12 da jami'an gwamnati ko kuma tsoffin jami'ai sun mutu sakamakon cutar har zuwa ranar 17 ga watan Maris.
Har zuwa 23 ga watan Maris, Iran na samun sabbin mutane 50 a kowace awa kuma tana samun sabon mutum daya da ke mutuwa a kowane minti goma saboda cutar coronavirus.
Ma'aikatan WHO sun ce akwai yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar sau biyar a Iran fiye da yadda aka ruwaito.
Ya kuma nuna cewa takunkumin Amurka kan Iran na iya shafar ikon kasar wajen magance cutar.
Babban Kwamishinan 'Yancin Dan Adam na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya bukaci a sassauta takunkumin tattalin arziki ga kasashen da cutar ta fi shafa, ciki har da Iran.
An tabbatar da barkewar cutar a Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu, lokacin da wasu matafiya biyu 'yan kasar Sin suka gwada tabbatacciyar cutar SARS-CoV-2 a Rome.
Lamarin ya fara ƙaruwa sosai, wanda ya sa gwamnatin Italiya ta dakatar da duk jiragen da ke zuwa da kuma daga China kuma ta ayyana dokar ta baci.
An gano wasu clusters na marasa alaƙa da COVID-19 daga baya, farawa da 16 da aka tabbatar a Lombardy a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu. A ranar 22 ga Fabrairu, Majalisar Ministocin ta ba da sanarwar sabon dokar dokar da za ta hana barkewar cutar, gami da keɓe mutane sama da 50,000 daga gundumomi 11 daban-daban a arewacin Italiya.
Firayim Minista Giuseppe Conte ya ce, "A yankunan da cutar ta addabi, ba za a yarda da shiga ko fita ba.
An kuma umarci dakatar da ayyukan aiki da wasanni a yankin. "A ranar 4 ga watan Maris, gwamnatin Italiya ta umarci rufe dukkan makarantu da jami'o'i a duk fadin kasar yayin da Italiya ta kai adadin mutuwar mutum 100.
Duk manyan wasannin wasanni, ciki har da wasannin kwallon kafa na Serie A, ya kamata a gudanar da su a rufe har zuwa watan Afrilu, amma a ranar 9 ga Maris, an dakatar da duk wasannin gaba daya na akalla wata daya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, Firayim Minista Conte ya ba da umarnin dakatar da kusan duk ayyukan kasuwanci ban da manyan kantuna da kantin magani. A ranar 6 ga Maris, Kwalejin Anaesthesia, Analgesia, Resuscitation da Rape na Italiya (SIAARTI) ta buga takardar shaidar ɗabi'a game da hanyoyin da za a iya amfani da su.
A ranar 19 ga watan Maris, Italiya ta zarce China a matsayin kasa da ke da yawan mutuwar coronavirus a duniya bayan da ta bayar da rahoton mutuwar mutane 3,405 daga cutar.
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, an ruwaito cewa Rasha ta aika da jiragen sama tara na soja dauke da kayan aikin likita zuwa Italiya.
Ya zuwa ranar 5 ga Afrilu, an sami mutane 128,948 da suka kamu da cutar, 15,887 sun mutu, kuma 21,815 sun warke a Italiya, tare da yawancinsu a lardin Lombardy.
Wani rahoto na CNN ya nuna cewa haɗuwa da yawan tsofaffi a Italiya da rashin iya gwajin duk wanda ya kamu da cutar har zuwa yau na iya zama mai ba da gudummawa ga yawan mutuwar.
Amsar da Burtaniya ta bayar ga cutar da farko ta bayyana a matsayin ɗaya daga cikin ƙasashe masu saurin kamuwa da cutar, kuma har zuwa 18 ga Maris, 2020, gwamnatin Burtaniya ba ta sanya kowane nau'i na nisantar jama'a ko matakan keɓewa ga jama'arta ba.
A sakamakon haka, gwamnati ta fuskanci suka saboda rashin saurin da kuma sahihancin martani ga damuwar da al'umma ke fuskanta. A ranar 16 ga Maris, Firayim Minista Boris Johnson ya yi sanarwa da ke ba da shawarar kauce wa duk tafiye-tafiye marasa mahimmanci da hulɗa da jama'a, yana ba da shawarar mutane suyi aiki daga gida idan za su iya kuma su guji wurare kamar mashaya, gidajen cin abinci, da gidajen wasan kwaikwayo.
A ranar 20 ga Maris, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa duk wuraren shakatawa kamar mashaya da dakin motsa jiki ya kamata a rufe su da wuri-wuri, kuma ta yi alƙawarin biyan kashi 80% na albashin ma'aikata har zuwa iyakar £2,500 a wata don kauce wa rashin aikin yi a cikin rikicin. A ranar 23 ga Maris, Firayim Minista ya sanar da tsauraran matakan nisantar zamantakewar jama'a, ya hana taron mutane sama da biyu da kuma iyakance tafiye-tafiye da ayyukan waje ga waɗanda aka ƙayyade da gaske.
Ba kamar matakan da suka gabata ba, 'yan sanda ne ke tilasta wannan takunkumin ta hanyar fitar da karar da kuma dakatar da taron.
An umarci yawancin kasuwancin da za a rufe, tare da keɓewa ga kasuwancin da aka ɗauka "mahimmanci", gami da manyan kantuna, kantin magani, bankuna, shagunan kayan aiki, tashoshin mai, da kuma wuraren aiki.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an tabbatar da farkon sanannen cutar COVID-19 a jihar Pacific ta Arewa maso Yammacin Washington a cikin wani mutum da ya dawo daga Wuhan a ranar 15 ga watan Janairu.
An kafa rukunin jami'an kula da cutar korona a ranar 29 ga watan Janairu.
A ranar 31 ga watan Janairu, gwamnatin Trump ta ayyana dokar ta baci ta lafiyar jama'a, kuma ta sanya takunkumin hana shiga balaguro daga China.
A ranar 28 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka - babbar cibiyar kiwon lafiyar jama'a ta gwamnatin Amurka - ta sanar da cewa sun kirkiro nasu saitin gwajin.
Duk da haka, Amurka ta fara jinkirin gwadawa, wanda ke kare ainihin yanayin annobar a halin yanzu.
Gwajin ya shafi lalacewar kayan gwajin da gwamnatin tarayya ta samar a watan Fabrairu, rashin samun amincewar gwamnati ga kayan gwajin da ba na gwamnati ba (na jami'o'i, kamfanoni da asibitoci) har zuwa karshen watan Fabrairu, da kuma tsauraran ka'idoji ga mutanen da suka cancanci yin gwajin har zuwa farkon watan Maris (ana bukatar shawarar likita bayan haka).
Har zuwa ranar 27 ga watan Fabrairu, jaridar Washington Post ta ruwaito cewa an yi gwaje-gwaje kasa da 4,000 a Amurka.
Har zuwa 13 ga Maris, The Atlantic ta ruwaito cewa an yi gwaje-gwaje kasa da 14,000.
A ranar 22 ga Maris, kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya ruwaito cewa: "Mutane da dama da ke fama da alamun cutar da umarnin likita sun jira sa'o'i ko kwanaki don a gwada su". Bayan an samu mutuwar farko a Amurka a jihar Washington a ranar 29 ga Fabrairu, Gwamna Jay Inslee ya ayyana dokar ta baci, ba da daɗewa ba sauran jihohi suka bi sahun.
Makarantu a yankin Seattle sun soke karatu a ranar 3 ga Maris, kuma a tsakiyar watan Maris, makarantu a duk faɗin ƙasar sun rufe. A ranar 6 ga Maris, 2020, an ba da hasashen tasirin sabon coronavirus a Amurka ta hanyar ƙungiyar masu ilimin cututtukan cuta a Imperial College London.
A wannan ranar ne Shugaba Trump ya sanya hannu kan Dokar Karin Kuɗi don Shirye-shirye da Amsa Coronavirus, wanda ya samar da dala biliyan 8.3 a cikin kudaden gaggawa ga hukumomin gwamnati don amsa cutar.
Kamfanoni sun kafa takunkumin hana ma'aikata tafiya, sun soke taro, kuma sun karfafa ma'aikata su yi aiki daga gida.
An soke wasanni da kuma lokutan wasanni. A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Trump ya sanar da dakatar da tafiye-tafiye zuwa ga yawancin yankuna na Turai ban da United Kingdom, na tsawon kwanaki 30, daga ranar 13 ga watan Maris.
Washegari, ya faɗaɗa takunkumin ya haɗa da Ƙasar Ingila da Ireland.
