A ranar 25 ga Maris, gwamnan ya ce nesa da jama'a na da tasiri, yayin da kimar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar ta fara raguwa daga kwanaki 2.0 zuwa kwanaki 4.7.
A ranar 28 ga Maris, an tabbatar da mutane 32,308 a Birnin New York, kuma mutane 672 sun mutu daga cutar. A ranar 26 ga Maris, Amurka ta ba da rahoton cewa tana da ƙarin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus fiye da kowace ƙasa a duniya, gami da China da Italiya.
Kamar yadda kafofin watsa labarai suka ruwaito a ranar 30 ga watan Maris, Shugaba Trump na Amurka ya yanke shawarar tsawaita ka'idojin nisantar jama'a har zuwa ranar 30 ga watan Afrilu.
A wannan rana, jirgin asibiti mai ɗauke da gado guda 1,000, wato, USNS Comfort, ya sauka a New York.
