Dalibai 'yan kasar Sin a jami'o'in Amurka sun hada kai don taimakawa wajen kai agaji zuwa yankunan da cutar ta addabi kasar Sin, tare da wasu kungiyoyi a yankin Chicago da aka ruwaito sun samu nasarar kai takunkumin N95 50,000 zuwa asibitoci a lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga watan Janairu. Kungiyar agaji ta Direct Relief, tare da hadin gwiwa da FedEx, ta kai takunkumin rufe fuska 200,000 tare da sauran kayan kariya na mutum, ciki har da safofin hannu da riguna, ta hanyar jigilar kayayyaki na gaggawa ta iska zuwa asibitin Wuhan Union a ranar 30 ga watan Janairu.
