Tedros ya kara da cewa "mu ne mafi karfi a sarkar da muke da rauni" kuma ya bukaci al'ummar duniya da su "saka hannun jari a yanzu ko kuma su biya daga baya".A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO a wani taron manema labarai ta sanya sunan cutar COVID-19 a matsayin sunan cutar.
A wannan ranar, Tedros ya ce Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya Antonio Guterres ya amince ya ba da "ikon da dukan tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ke da shi a matsayin martani".
Sakamakon haka an kunna tawagar gudanar da rikicin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda ya ba da damar daidaita aikin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda WHO ta ce zai ba su damar "mai da hankali kan aikin kiwon lafiya yayin da sauran hukumomi za su iya kawo ƙwarewarsu don magance mummunan tasirin zamantakewar al'umma, tattalin arziki da ci gaba daga annobar".
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, an kunna wani Kungiyar Haɗin gwiwa ta China da WHO ke jagoranta don samar da ƙwarewar duniya da WHO a cikin filin a China don taimakawa cikin gudanar da cikin gida da kuma kimanta "yanayin cutar da yaduwar cutar" ta hanyar gudanar da bita da tarurruka tare da manyan cibiyoyin matakin ƙasa da kuma gudanar da ziyarar bita don kimanta "tasirin ayyukan mayar da martani a yankuna da ƙauyuka, gami da birane da ƙauyuka".A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta bayyana cewa "duniya dole ne ta yi ƙarin shirye-shirye don yiwuwar cutar ta coronavirus" ta bayyana cewa duk da cewa har yanzu da wuri don a kira ta annoba, ƙasashe ya kamata su kasance "a cikin shiri".
