An tabbatar da kasancewar kwayar a cikin samfurin ta hanyar RT-PCR, wanda ke gano RNA na coronavirus.
Wannan gwajin na musamman ne kuma an tsara shi ne don gano kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 RNA kawai.
Ana amfani da gwajin ne wajen tabbatar da cewa akwai sabon kamuwa da cuta ko kuma yana aiki.
