Amfani da kayan aikin wanke hannu na barasa akai-akai na iya haifar da bushewar fata sai dai idan an kara emollients da/ko moisturizers a cikin tsari.
Za a iya rage ko kawar da tasirin busassun giya ta hanyar ƙara glycerin da/ko wasu emollients a cikin tsari.
A gwajin asibiti, maganin wanke hannu na barasa wanda ke dauke da emollients ya haifar da raguwar damuwa da bushewa a fata idan aka kwatanta da sabulu ko na'urar wankewa.
