A shekara ta 2008, wani bincike da aka yi daga Jami'ar Westminster, London, kuma masana'antar tawul ɗin ta tallafa masa, wato, Tissue Symposium na Turai, ya gwada tsabtar da ake samu a lokacin amfani da tawul ɗin takarda, na'urar bushe hannu mai zafi da na'urar bushe hannu mai iska mai iska.
Bayan wankewa da bushewa da mai bushewar iska, an sami karuwar ƙwayoyin cuta a ƙasan yatsunsu da kashi 194% kuma a hannun hannu da kashi 254%.
Drying tare da mai bushe iska yana haifar da ƙaruwa a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta a kan yatsunsu na matsakaici na 42% da kuma a kan hannu na 15%.
