Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) shine enzyme wanda ke haɗuwa da waje (mambran sel) na sel a cikin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda da hanji.
ACE2 yana fuskantar aikin enzyme mai canza angiotensin (ACE) wanda ke da alaƙa da rage adadin angiotensin-II da haɓaka Ang ((1-7)) yana mai da shi magani mai yiwuwa wanda za'a yi niyya don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin cibiyar shigar da kwayar halitta ga wasu coronaviruses.
An kira kwayar halitta na ɗan adam hACE2.
Angiotensin 2 mai canza enzyme shine zinc wanda ke dauke da metaloenzyme wanda ke kan endothelium da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Kwayar ACE2 tana dauke da wani yanki na M2 N-terminal peptidase da kuma wani yanki na C-terminal renal amino acid transporter colectin.
ACE2 shine mai amfani da hanyar 1 na membrane mai amfani da hanya guda, tare da yankin aikin enzyme wanda aka fallasa akan kwayoyin halitta a cikin huhu da sauran kayan.
Yankin waje na ACE2 yana manne da yankin transmembrane ta wani enzyme da ake kira sheddase, kuma an saki samfurin furotin mai narkewa zuwa cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe an sanya shi cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin yawancin gabobin jiki: ACE2 yana haɗe da membrane na yawancin kwayoyin alveolus na nau'in II na huhu, entrositic na ƙananan hanji, arteries da ƙwayoyin endothelium na veins da ƙwayoyin tsoka na arteries a yawancin gabobin jiki.
Hakanan ana samun bayyanar mRNA ACE2 a cikin cerebral cortex, striatum, hypothalamus da kuma kwakwalwar kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine yayi aiki azaman mai daidaitawa ga ACE.
ACE tana ɗaure da hormone I na angiotensin zuwa cikin narkewar angiotensin II.
ACE2 a madadin haka yana manne da carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) da kuma hydrolysis zuwa cikin angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 na iya kuma manne wa wasu peptides da suka hada da [des-Arg9]-bradikinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana daidaita rarraba membrane mai ɗaukar amino acid mai tsaka tsaki SLC6A19 kuma an nuna shi a cikin cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin mai wucewa, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban cibiyar shigarwa cikin ƙwayoyin cuta don wasu ƙwayoyin cuta ciki har da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus wanda ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (virus wanda ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, ɗaure ga sunadarai na S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 a kan yankin enzyme na ACE2 a saman ƙwayoyin halitta yana haifar da endosytosis da kuma sauya kwayar cutar da enzyme zuwa cikin endosomes da ke tsakanin ƙwayoyin.
Tsarin shigarwa kuma yana buƙatar ƙirar furotin S ta hanyar gyaran sararin samaniya na TMPRSS2, mai haɓaka wanda ke ƙarƙashin binciken yanzu a matsayin mai yuwuwar magani. Wannan ya haifar da wasu yin hasashen cewa rage matakan ACE2 a cikin sel na iya taimakawa wajen yaƙar kamuwa da cuta.
Koyaya, ƙungiyoyi da ƙungiyoyi masu ƙwarewa da hukumomi masu tsarawa suna ba da shawarar ci gaba da daidaitaccen ACE da maganin ARB.
Binciken tsarin da meta-analysis da aka buga a ranar 11 ga Yuli 2012 sun gano cewa "amfani da magungunan ACE yana da alaƙa da raguwar 34% mai mahimmanci a cikin haɗarin cutar huhu idan aka kwatanta da na sarrafawa".
